<p><em>This thread is 100% sponsored and approved by our lord <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=304355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1528252495" alt="Silberescher" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=304355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;">Silberescher</a></span>.</em></p>
<hr />
<p>Hi, I'm Cy. You might have seen my <a href="http://sexycontainmentprocedures.tumblr.com/tagged/cosplay">cosplays</a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-83823-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-83823-1')">1</a></sup> floating around Tumblr sometimes, or perhaps just on my <a href="/sexycontainmentprocedures">author page.</a> I spend quite a bit of time and effort making things like the D-class jumpsuit or <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/KeterCrafts">ID cards.</a> So far I've gone to two cons &#8212; Anime Midwest in 2016 and Animazement in 2017 &#8212; in either a D-class jumpsuit, <a href="/scp-2156">SCP-2156</a> makeup, or field operative tactical gear and gotten recognized by more than a few passerby. I even made myself <a href="https://usercontent.irccloud-cdn.com/file/wnkkaBp9/irccloudcapture412795090.jpg">business cards</a> for 2017's con (and to hand out when people IRL ask me what my <a href="http://sexycontainmentprocedures.tumblr.com/post/160169791087/long-overdue-cosplay-x-car-post">car</a> is about) so that I could maybe bring some new traffic to the site!</p>
<p>The purpose of this thread is to get everyone's awesome cosplay in one place so that we can marvel at our collective glory. So when posting, keep in mind:</p>
<ul>
<li>Keep it SFW or warn accordingly</li>
<li>Talk about how you made the outfit happen if you want!</li>
<li>Feel free to include propmaking stuff as well, it's all part of the cosplay world!</li>
</ul>
<p>You can do collapsible images, a paragraph of talking about yourself that's cluttered with hyperlinks like what I did, or anything similar. You get the picture.</p>
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="title">Footnotes</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-83823-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-83823-1')">1</a>. Obligatory warning that my blog sometimes contains NSFW stuff and the cosplay tag there has some NSFW-ish joke pictures starting on the second page.</div>
</div>

