<p>Hey it's your friendly neighborhood Lex1nat0r here with some terrible phone pictures of my SCP cosplay labcoat. A friend and I have been doing SCP cosplay at a couple of cons for like three years now, so if you see a pair of researchers at PAX East or Anime Boston it might be us. We sometimes also have another friend as a D-class/magical girl in tow, I'll see about getting info from his cosplay to put up here.</p>
